  "subject": "Initialize HttpClient as bean",
  "commit_message": "Initialize HttpClient as bean\n\n- move the HttpClient initialization ouf of RestUtil into it's\n  own HttpClientConfig @Configuration class\n- this avoids reinitialization of the class on every request\n- this also makes sure that the trace context is preserved\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4239\nChange-Id: I1607a089581e0c98822d776946c680649269d126\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
